== 使用方法 ==
<code>{{tlp|Bold link if not equal|string1|string2|link|caption}}</code> gives
* "'''[[hyperlink|caption]]'''" (i.e. bold link) if <code>string1</code> and <code>string2</code> are not equal,
* "caption" (i.e. plain and no link) if they are.

